      "content": {
        "title": "Noncompetitive and Uncompetitive Inhibition",
        "definition": "Inhibition modes in which the inhibitor binds away from (noncompetitive) or only to (uncompetitive) the enzyme–substrate complex, altering Vmax and/or Km distinct from competitive patterns.",
